profile_summary:
Ayush Raj is a highly skilled software developer with a strong foundation in programming languages such as C++, Python, and JavaScript. As a passionate coding enthusiast with a background in robotics, Ayush possesses a unique combination of technical expertise and innovative thinking. With a remarkable academic record and a GPA of 9+, Ayush has consistently demonstrated exceptional problem-solving skills and a keen eye for detail.

As a software trainee with the elite Horizon Mars Rover Team at CUSAT, Ayush has honed his skills in collaborative development and real-world application of state-of-the-art technologies. With an active presence on GitHub, showcasing 44 public repositories and an influence among 4 followers, Ayush has established himself as a credible and reliable professional in the development community. By combining his technical prowess with a relentless passion for coding and robotics, Ayush delivers cutting-edge solutions that drive innovation and advance the boundaries of what is possible.
